# Future Features Backlog (Phase 2+)

All the advanced mechanics from the original v5.0 will be added here, one at a time:

### Phase 2 – Economy Depth
- Multiple goods (TECH, CLOTH, LUXURY)
- Factories + upgrades + retooling
- Land claiming + rental system
- Market prices driven by preferences

### Phase 3 – Agents & Survival
- Hunger / starvation / death
- Role system (Wanderer, Owner, Producer, Landlord, Renter, Subsister)
- Basic DNA traits (no evolution yet)
- Foraging on idle land + drought mechanic

### Phase 4 – Evolution & Stats
- Generation system + extinction / next gen
- DNA inheritance + mutation
- Comprehensive stats popup (tabs, charts, reports)
- Full save/load + export/import

### Phase 5 – Polish & Advanced
- Exploration / pathfinding
- Interaction history between agents
- Gini coefficient + wealth distribution graphs
- Performance optimizations

We will implement these one feature at a time after Phase 1 is solid.
